  ENDDO.
 
*==============================

* Evaluate Asset Creation

*==============================

  DATA(lv_asset_success) = abap_false.
 
  IF lt_asset IS NOT INITIAL.

    lv_asset_success = abap_true.

  ENDIF.
 
  IF lv_asset_success = abap_false.

    APPEND VALUE #( type = 'E' message = 'Asset creation failed. PR not updated.' ) TO et_return.

    RETURN.

  ENDIF.
 
*==============================

* Commit Assets

*==============================

  CALL FUNCTION 'BAPI_TRANSACTION_COMMIT'

    EXPORTING

      wait = 'X'.
 
